A simple openerp installation script.

* Includes openerp server and web client.
* Installs all necesary packages. 
* Stores data in /opt/openerp with "openerp" user (default password: "openerp") 
* Installs start/stop scrips in init.d.
* Automamatically stars and stops openerp server and client

Tested in ubuntu 10.04
                        
Based on:

http://www.theopensourcerer.com/2011/04/19/how-to-install-openerp-6-on-ubuntu-10-04-lts-server-part-1/